{
  "name": "next-auth",
  "version": "0.1.0",
  "private": true,
  "scripts": {

  "devDependencies": {
    "@babel/core": "^7.13.10",
    "@storybook/addon-actions": "^6.1.21",

    "@storybook/addon-links": "^6.1.21",

    "eslint-plugin-react-hooks": "^4.2.0",
    "husky": "^5.1.3",
    "jest": "^26.6.3",
    "jest-styled-components": "^7.0.3",
    "lint-staged": "^10.5.4",
    "prettier": "^2.2.1",
    "typescript": "^4.2.3"

  "lint-staged": {
    "src/**/*": [
